WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Let this arrive as material already held, not as a task to solve.

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:17.000
Take a few measured breaths, letting the exhale be slightly longer.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:34.000
The week can be present as a field of continuity before it becomes explanation.

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:48.000
Let the field settle around what is already known.

00:00:50.000 --> 00:01:00.000
Notice one body response and leave the rest unforced.
